Package: peruflorads43
Type: Package
Title: Check Threatened Plant Species Status Against Peru's Supreme
        Decree 043-2006-AG
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Paul E.", family = "Santos Andrade", role
        = c("aut", "cre"), email = "paulefrens@gmail.com", comment =
        c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375")))
Maintainer: Paul E. Santos Andrade <paulefrens@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools to match plant species names against the
        official threatened species list of Peru (Supreme Decree
        043-2006-AG, 2006). Implements a hierarchical matching pipeline
        with exact, fuzzy, and suffix matching algorithms to handle
        naming variations and taxonomic changes. Supports both the
        original 2006 nomenclature and updated taxonomic names,
        allowing users to check protection status regardless of
        nomenclatural changes since the decree's publication. Threat
        categories follow International Union for Conservation of
        Nature standards (Critically Endangered, Endangered,
        Vulnerable, Near Threatened).
Encoding: UTF-8
